        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Golf and Coca-Cola might seem like an unusual pairing at first glance, but the new Malbon x Coca-Cola collection seamlessly blends these two icons into a collaboration that celebrates heritage, style, and community. This exclusive range is available at TrendyGolf, and continues to honor Coca-Cola's iconic legacy while introducing a fresh, nostalgic twist to your golfing wardrobe.</p>"
          }
