          "settings": {
            "text": "KEY PIECES IN THE COLLECTION",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Spencerian Block T-Shirt</strong>: Made from soft cotton jersey, this tee features a ribbed neckline and a front chest pocket with a Coke Buckets screenprint. The Spencerian Block logo on the back and woven flag label add a touch of iconic style.<br/><br/><strong>x Coca Cola Ice Cold Hoodie:</strong> The Malbon x Coca-Cola Ice Cold Hoodie offers comfort with its 100% cotton fleece construction and self-lined hoodie. Featuring a front pocket, ribbed hem and cuffs, and unique embroidery details including the Ice Cold logo and M Script bottle cap.</p><p><strong>International Shorts</strong>: Crafted from poly-coated nylon, these shorts offer durability and comfort with an elastic waistband, hidden zippered pockets, and an all-over print. Embroidered logos enhance their sporty look.</p><p><strong>Spencerian Block Shoe Bag</strong>: Durable vinyl and velour construction with a secure zipper, inner pocket, and handle make this bag both practical and stylish. It features the Spencerian Block and Coca-Cola logos.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
